title: Martha's
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Western, Fast food, Juice bar, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Focuses on natural fast foods and has breakfast menu, hot rolls, salad boxes, wraps, salads, soups, juices, and smoothies. Coded menu with DF for dairyfree, VG for vegan, and a note that it can substitute yogurt with soya yogurt. For vegans a falafel wrap or salad box (with the soya yogurt and vegan slaw subs), 4 vegan salads which are packed with all sorts of grains, noodles, nuts, vegetables, and seeds, hummus & flat bread, and usually a soup is vegan.
